<div class="cards">
  <div id="cardOne" class= card>
    <h2>Teaching</h2>
    
    <p>Are you a passionate and experienced yoga instructor or meditation practitioner? Share your expertise with our veteran patrons at Healing Warriors. By volunteering your time and skills, you play a crucial role in guiding veterans through their physical and mental healing journey. Your dedication to teaching breathwork, hatha yoga, and meditation can profoundly impact their lives, providing them with the tools to cope with challenges and find peace within. Join us in fostering a supportive environment where veterans can rediscover their inner strength and resilience.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div id="cardTwo" class= card>
    <h2>Hosting</h2>
    
    <p>If you believe in the healing power of yoga, breathwork, and meditation for veterans, consider becoming a vital part of Healing Warriors by hosting a location. By offering your space, whether it's a studio, community center, or any suitable venue in the Greater Houston Area, you can help us expand our reach and impact even more lives. Your contribution as a host ensures that our free teachings and consultations are accessible to veterans seeking solace and recovery. Join us in creating a sanctuary of healing for those who have served our country and become an essential pillar of support in our mission.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div id="cardThree" class= card>
    <h2>Sharing</h2>
    
    <p>Spread the word about Healing Warriors and the invaluable services we offer to veterans in the Greater Houston Area. Your voice can make a difference by reaching more individuals in need. Help us create awareness on social media platforms by sharing our mission, success stories, and upcoming events. Additionally, consider speaking about Healing Warriors in your community, workplace, or amongst friends and family. Together, we can raise awareness about the importance of mental and physical well-being for veterans and extend the reach of our healing resources to those who may benefit from them. Your support as a messenger is instrumental in making a positive impact on the lives of our courageous veterans.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
